reviewText: Good for entertainment. But some of the stuff this guy does is for someone trained in Covert or Special OPs. Some stuff the regular guy can do. Some stuff unless you are an ex Ranger, Marine, Green Beret or SEAL you can't do. Like swing across a river onto a bridge with a grappling hook. Yet very interesting, informative and entertaining.
Yes, it sure did! I watched it one time on the history channel and tried to find it. U were the only ones that had it and I am GREATFUL! Thank u!
